entries.title: The private angst over Donald Trump’s racist attacks on Elaine Chao goes public
entries.description: His rhetoric “says a whole lot more about him than it will ever say about Asian Americans.”

entries.title: Mitch Daniels on Senate bid: 'I'm worried about winning it and regretting it'
entries.description: Daniels insists politics is not on his mind as he takes meetings on a potential Senate bid, saying he wants to figure out if the upper chamber "fits" him.
